<item>
            <title>[SYNAPSE-951] EndpointDefinition Serialization issue</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SYNAPSE-951</link>
                <project id="12310201" key="SYNAPSE">Synapse</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;&amp;lt;endpoint name=&quot;EchoServiceEp&quot;&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
   &amp;lt;address uri=&quot;http://10.200.3.190:8281/services/echo&quot;&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
      &amp;lt;timeout&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
         &amp;lt;duration&amp;gt;2000&amp;lt;/duration&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
      &amp;lt;/timeout&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
      &amp;lt;suspendOnFailure&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
         &amp;lt;initialDuration&amp;gt;60000&amp;lt;/initialDuration&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
         &amp;lt;progressionFactor&amp;gt;2.0&amp;lt;/progressionFactor&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
      &amp;lt;/suspendOnFailure&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
      &amp;lt;markForSuspension&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
         &amp;lt;errorCodes&amp;gt;101000,101500&amp;lt;/errorCodes&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
         &amp;lt;retriesBeforeSuspension&amp;gt;3&amp;lt;/retriesBeforeSuspension&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
      &amp;lt;/markForSuspension&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
      &amp;lt;retryConfig&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
         &amp;lt;disabledErrorCodes&amp;gt;101507,101509&amp;lt;/disabledErrorCodes&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
      &amp;lt;/retryConfig&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
   &amp;lt;/address&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&amp;lt;/endpoint&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;p&gt;When the above endpoint configuration is serialized, unnecessary &amp;lt;responseAction/&amp;gt; element get added to &amp;lt;timeout&amp;gt; section as follows.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    &amp;lt;timeout&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
          &amp;lt;duration&amp;gt;2000&amp;lt;/duration&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
           &amp;lt;responseAction/&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
     &amp;lt;/timeout&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This makes the configuration invalid and configuration built failure.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
